PREDLAŽEM DA MI DOPUSTITE.

18
00:02:20,637 --> 00:02:22,183
UPADAJ!

19
00:02:23,677 --> 00:02:26,256
VI TO MENI PRETITE?
- UPADAJ!

20
00:02:32,752 --> 00:02:34,377
PA-PA.

21
00:02:48,101 --> 00:02:52,568
